# gravify

**gravify** is a simple package to generate
[Gravatar](https://en.gravatar.com/) URLs. :link:

```py
>>> user = Gravatar("example@example.com")
>>> user.url
'https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/23463b99b62a72f26ed677cc556c44e8'
```

